* phase-6 part-2 relocation test: a section-relative (relocatable) program.
* Each address that names a label generates a B$RELOC directive (section 0,
* RELOCOP add); STA START*2 additionally carries EVALOP=MULT/VALUE=2, so its
* directive is the 3-word general form.  DATA's OCT word is absolute (no reloc).
       OUNAME RELTEST
START  LDA   DATA
       ADA   DATA+1
       STA   START*2
DATA   OCT   123
       TRA   START
       END
